Package: GenITR
Type: Package
Title: Learning and Inference for Generalized Individualized Treatment Rules
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Muxuan", "Liang", , "mliang2@mdanderson.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides methods for estimating generalized individualized treatment rules
    and conducting inference on the value of estimated treatment rules.
    The package includes concordance-based estimation, kernel-based methods,
    and supporting utilities for simulation studies and real data analysis.
